The [[Bayer designation]] '''Omicron Canis Majoris''' (ο CMa / ο Canis Majoris) is shared by two [[star]]s, in the [[constellation]] [[Canis Major]]: *[[Omicron1 Canis Majoris|ο¹ Canis Majoris]] *[[Omicron2 Canis Majoris|ο² Canis Majoris]] They are separated by 2.06° on the sky.
ο¹ Canis Majoris was member of asterism 軍市 (Jūn Shì), ''Market for Soldiers'', ''[[Well (Chinese constellation)|Well]]'' mansion.<ref>{{zh icon}} [http://aeea.nmns.edu.tw/2006/0607/ap060716.html AEEA (Activities of Exhibition and Education in Astronomy) 天文教育資訊網 2006 年 7 月 16 日]</ref> ο² Canis Majoris was not any member of asterism.
